{
  "logNo": "110173596586",
  "title": "오대산 소금강 오토캠핑장에서의 짧은 휴가",
  "addDate": "2013. 8. 6.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110173596586",
  "html_size": 208978,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110173596586\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110173596586\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">&#65279;휴가일정은 애들과 애들엄마의 일정에 맞춰</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">짧게 다녀오기로 합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">어디로 갈까?<br />이번 여름 휴가는</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">4살, 6살 애들을 데리고 2박3일 캠핑장에 도전하기로 합의!</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">장소는 오대산 소금강오토캠핑장을 선택합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">이유는</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">1. 강원도 숲속이고, 계곡이 좋다 (라고들 한다)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">2. 바닷가(주문진)가 가까워서 바다도 볼 수 있다 (애들 엄마의&nbsp;오래된 여행테마죠. 탁트인 바다!!!)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">3. 새로 보수공사를 했다고 하고, 국립이라 야영장 시설이 괜찮을 것 같다</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">7월에 예약이 오픈되자마자 광클릭!! </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">화장실 바로 옆 개수대가 가까운 일반영지 자리(B013)를 예약합니다. (전기를 쓸 수 있는 자동차영지도 예약했지만, 1박2일만 성공해서 예약취소)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">애들 데리고 2일이나 잠을 자야하니까 여러가지 준비를 합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">멀리 갔는데, 애들이 '여기서 못자겠어, 집에가자~' 라고 울고 떼쓰기 시작하면 휴가 망치는 겁니다. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그래서 빠진건 없는지 확인, 또 확인합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">토요일 애들 엄마 퇴근 후 바로 출발. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">다행히 차는 안막힙니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">토요일 10시 언저리에 야영장에 도착해서 텐트만 후다닥 치고 잠을 잡니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">다행히 애들도 낯설어하지 않고 잘 잡니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">다음날 아침. 텐트를 옮기고, 타프를 설치하고, 테이블과 의자 펴고, 해먹걸고. 등등. 남은 기간을 위한 세팅을 합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7f10fa80f8638ab9.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_250/isuhani_1375767305037uaQi8_JPEG/IMG_3937.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7f10fa80f8638ab9.jpg\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">간단하게 낮동안 놀다 오던 지난달과 비교하면, 짐이 좀 늘었습니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">자동차에 다 실렸다는게 신기할 따름이죠 ^^</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">예약할 때 분명히 화장실 바로 옆이었는데, 실제 와보니, 화장실이 있어야 할 자리에 개수대가 있네요. 화장실은 주차장 건너편. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">화장실이 조금 멀어서 애들 화장실 갈 때 불편함이 있지만, 개수대 옆이라서 애들에게는 또다른 재미가 있네요.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c9c297d624ea6d2e.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_69/isuhani_1375766902125s9kQB_JPEG/IMG_3912.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c9c297d624ea6d2e.jpg\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">애들을 재우려니까. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">바람에 안불려야겠고 (학암포 갔다가 조그만 그늘막텐트 날아갈까, 폴대 뿌러질까&nbsp;걱정했던 때가&nbsp;있었죠)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">비와도 방수가 잘 되야겠고, </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">치기쉬워야겠더라구요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그래서 자동텐트 저렴한걸로 하나 구입합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">설치해보니. 너무 큰가 싶기도 한데, 애들이 커갈테니 나중을 위해서 ok. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c90d6a496bc73652.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_239/isuhani_1375767141179M4rME_JPEG/IMG_4066.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c90d6a496bc73652.jpg\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">애들 좋아하는 해먹도 하나 삽니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">부피가 작은 패러슈트재질의 해먹, 대형사이즈로 구매.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5e025d1f44c5994c.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_9/isuhani_1375767402240L6zMQ_JPEG/IMG_3983.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5e025d1f44c5994c.jpg\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">애들용으로 싸고 작은 의자를 사고, 부부는 릴렉스체어를 사서 가지고 다녔죠.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그런데, 애들이 자기들도 머리가 받쳐지는 의자를 사달라고 조릅니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">어디 놀러가면 자<br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />기들이 릴렉스체어를 차지하고 부부는 애들용 의자에 앉거나 BBQ 의자에 앉아야 하는 신세 -.-;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그래서, 중고로 콜멘 슬림캡틴체어를 삽니다. 집 근처에서 직거래 할 수 있는 물건이 나왔길래 얼른 삽니다. ㅎㅎ</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">애들이 릴렉스 체어에 앉았을 때, 어른이 이 의자에 앉아도 허리 아프진 않을것 같아요. 실제 앉아보니 릴렉스체어와는 또다른 편함이 있더군요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">세팅도 끝나고, </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">아침밥도 해서 먹었습니다.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">자. 이제. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">구경가보자. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/de38329f0b5005a9.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_275/isuhani_1375767902425wFUCm_JPEG/IMG_3923.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/de38329f0b5005a9.jpg\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">일단 오전에는 오대산 등산을 하기로 합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">과자 한봉지 들고서 ㅎㅎㅎ</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">가볍게, 식당암 보고 오자. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">6살 아들이 '큰거', '빠른거', '쎈거'. 이런 최고에 대한 지향이 있습니다. 뭐 아이언맨 좋아하고, 스포츠카 좋아하고 그런거죠.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그래서 엄청 큰 바위가 있으니 그걸 보러 가자! 라고 꼬셨죠. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그러나 20분 걷다가 포기합니다. 더워요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">식당암까지 한시간은 더 걸릴 것 같은데, 딸은 자꾸 업어달라고 하고. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_265/isuhani_1375767902692TvjhW_JPEG/IMG_3926.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_265/isuhani_1375767902692TvjhW_JPEG/IMG_3926.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_265/isuhani_1375767902692TvjhW_JPEG/IMG_3926.JPG?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그냥. 바로 계곡으로 가자. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">이미 계곡에는 많은 사람들이 있네요.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">저 멀리 보이는 구름다리가 캠핑장에 연결되어 있는 다리네요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">캠핑장에서 수영복입고 계곡에서 물놀이. 물 시원하고 좋네요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">애들도 즐거워하고 ^^ </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bb36f434a2fe53b4.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_156/isuhani_1375768320686M4yEF_JPEG/IMG_3933.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bb36f434a2fe53b4.jpg\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">계곡에서 더 놀다 가자고 절규하는 애들을 살살 달래서 텐트로 돌아와서 점심을 먹습니다. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">딸애가 케익용 칼을 들고 엄마 도와주겠다고 준비합니다. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">점심을 간단하게 먹고 주문진으로 갑니다. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">원래는 신혼시절 주문진항에서 생선구이 먹었던 추억이 있어서 생선구이를 먹으려 했죠.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">근데, 그 사이 주문진항 인근이 많이 정리되어서 예전 모습과 달라졌네요. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그래서, 그냥 회 먹기로 합니다. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/49409e91eb93afd8.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_269/isuhani_1375768808474wjeLO_JPEG/IMG_3941.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/49409e91eb93afd8.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">아들녀석이 카메라를 너무 가지고 싶어해서</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">저렴한 디카, 방수되는걸로 하나 사줬더니 여기저기서 사진을 마구 찍어댑니다. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">횟집에서도 사진찍기에 집중. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_152/isuhani_13757688087028UKKR_JPEG/IMG_3945.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_152/isuhani_13757688087028UKKR_JPEG/IMG_3945.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_152/isuhani_13757688087028UKKR_JPEG/IMG_3945.JPG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">우리나라의 바다는. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">제주도 바다가 최고. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그 다음은 동해 같아요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">오는길에 하나로 마트를 들러서 저녁꺼리와 다음날 먹을거리를 사고. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_5/isuhani_1375769057608ntkiQ_JPEG/IMG_3952.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_5/isuhani_1375769057608ntkiQ_JPEG/IMG_3952.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_5/isuhani_1375769057608ntkiQ_JPEG/IMG_3952.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">늦은 오후.</span></p><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1375769085783\"></span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1375769085783\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1375769087967\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1375769087967\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1375769089127\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1375769089127\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1375769089671\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1375769089671\">&#65279;딸 아이의 애교</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"> \r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_57/isuhani_1375769057865UqWIq_JPEG/IMG_3957.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_57/isuhani_1375769057865UqWIq_JPEG/IMG_3957.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_57/isuhani_1375769057865UqWIq_JPEG/IMG_3957.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>재롱</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_185/isuhani_1375769058232TwT4W_JPEG/IMG_3958.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_185/isuhani_1375769058232TwT4W_JPEG/IMG_3958.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_185/isuhani_1375769058232TwT4W_JPEG/IMG_3958.JPG?type=w3\"></p></span>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">아들은 여전히&nbsp;카메라 홀릭 중.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_26/isuhani_13757692321281VXRV_JPEG/IMG_3978.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_26/isuhani_13757692321281VXRV_JPEG/IMG_3978.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_26/isuhani_13757692321281VXRV_JPEG/IMG_3978.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">저녁준비를 시작합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">캠핑하면 역시 고기 구워먹는게 빠질 수 없죠. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">아빠가 숯을 준비합니다.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">가족이 단촐해서 숯도 조금이면 충분합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/772560ecc8cd7b38.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_173/isuhani_1375769232318NkAb9_JPEG/IMG_3981.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/772560ecc8cd7b38.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">아빠가 숯 준비하고 고기굽는 모습을 옆에서 지켜봅니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">여기는 요리학교. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">요리선생님이 요리하는 모습을 구경하고, 준비를 도와줄거예요</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">라는군요. ㅎㅎ</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">왠일로 얌전히 있는 딸. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">아들은.. 여전히 카메라 홀릭. ㅎㅎㅎ</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_104/isuhani_1375769509941Y0AoX_JPEG/IMG_3993.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_104/isuhani_1375769509941Y0AoX_JPEG/IMG_3993.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_104/isuhani_1375769509941Y0AoX_JPEG/IMG_3993.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">다음날 아침. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">커피 한잔하고.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_192/isuhani_1375769510092LDlRD_JPEG/IMG_3994.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_192/isuhani_1375769510092LDlRD_JPEG/IMG_3994.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_192/isuhani_1375769510092LDlRD_JPEG/IMG_3994.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>핸드폰으로 음악도 듣고</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_295/isuhani_1375769510284LgycK_JPEG/IMG_3995.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_295/isuhani_1375769510284LgycK_JPEG/IMG_3995.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130806_295/isuhani_1375769510284LgycK_JPEG/IMG_3995.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>애들을 위해서 계란을 삶습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>여유롭고 행복한 시간.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/cd02789669728f81.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_181/isuhani_1375769510460zsU33_JPEG/IMG_3999.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/cd02789669728f81.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>표정으로 장난치기를 좋아하는 딸.</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5a1ad2d079e04dc4.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_171/isuhani_1375769510652RXPbu_JPEG/IMG_4004.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5a1ad2d079e04dc4.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>다양한 표정을 지어봅니다.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/98732d3678f11f3b.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_299/isuhani_1375769865943sxbnl_JPEG/IMG_4013.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/98732d3678f11f3b.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>삶은 계란을 먹다가도 표정 장난은 멈추지 않아요.</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e48693509c9e6cc0.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_140/isuhani_1375769510876pe4hc_JPEG/IMG_4023.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e48693509c9e6cc0.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">아들은 저런 포즈를 잡고 싶어서</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">자기도 머리가 받쳐지는 의자가 필요하다는거죠. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">편해보이네요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">손에 쥔 과자 한봉지면 행복한가봅니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1f3af700f2655ff1.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130806_219/isuhani_13757699802001qFB5_JPEG/IMG_4029.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1f3af700f2655ff1.jpg\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">배가 부른 아이들을 위해서 애니메이션을 보여줍니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">전기가 없기 때문에 밧데리가 떨어질 때까지만 볼 수 있죠. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">저가형 노트북이라서 밧데리가 얼마 안가요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">어제 한시간 넘게 봤으니, 오늘은 얼마나 버텨주려나. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b31079c657e94b22.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130806_6/isuhani_1375769980407ks4A6_JPEG/IMG_4046.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6DBABAA')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b31079c657e94b22.jpg\"><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1375770048807\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1375770048807\">&#65279;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">애들이 애니메이션을 보는 동안 </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">부부는 디저트에 맥주를 마시면서 한가로운 시간을 보냅니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">자연속에서의 이 짧은 순간을 위해서 캠핑을 가는건가보다 싶습니다. ^^</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">이후 물놀이 한 번 더 하고, 또 밥을 먹고 놀다가 짐 챙기고 돌아왔네요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">가는 것보다, 짐 철수하고 돌아오는게 훠~~~~~~~~~얼 씬 힘들더라는.. -.-</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그래도, 애들에게 좋은 추억, 엄마아빠에겐 여유로운 시간이 되었던 휴가네요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
